 <refsection>
  <title>Description</title>
  <simpara>
   The file <filename>$PROJECT_ROOT/.config/project.nix</filename> contains the
   declarative specification of your Project Manager configuration. The command
   <command>project-manager</command> takes this file and realises the project
   environment configuration specified therein.
  </simpara>
 </refsection>
